717747f-a.text:
Broadway, south from but not including West 134th Street, showing the street in preparation for repaving. On the right, partially obscured by steam boiler is a 3-story brick house at the N.W. corner of West 133rd Street and south of it,a 5-story one, bearing No. 3289 Broadway, between
West 133rd and West 132nd Streets.
June 30, 1900.
Board of Transportation Photograph.
William B. Parsons Collection.
